737
01:12:11,589 --> 01:12:14,936
上城墙! 准备好灰!
On the walls! Prepare the ash!

738
01:12:25,677 --> 01:12:28,309
北面去十个人!
Ten men to the north side!

739
01:12:30,571 --> 01:12:32,261
发警报!
Send the warning!

740
01:12:35,347 --> 01:12:36,475
点上!
Light it!

741
01:12:51,500 --> 01:12:53,012
我们不是要待在这里吧?
Guess we're not getting out of here, huh?

742
01:12:53,085 --> 01:12:56,619
这不是要困住你们 是防止他进来
This isn't to keep you in. It's to keep him out.

743
01:12:56,734 --> 01:12:59,539
"他"是谁?
"Him" who?

744
01:13:12,605 --> 01:13:14,486
你是什么东西?
What are you?

745
01:13:15,927 --> 01:13:18,673
我不是东西 Ben 我是人
I'm not a "what," Ben. I'm a "who."

746
01:13:18,714 --> 01:13:20,831
你就是那个怪物
You're the monster.

747
01:13:20,862 --> 01:13:24,031
别纠缠于名字了
Let's not resort to name-calling.

748
01:13:31,017 --> 01:13:33,563
你利用我
You used me.

749
01:13:34,781 --> 01:13:37,061
你自己杀不了他
You couldn't kill him yourself,

750
01:13:37,292 --> 01:13:40,028
所以骗我来做
so you made me do it.

751
01:13:40,059 --> 01:13:43,233
我没有骗你做任何事
I didn't make you do anything.

752
01:13:46,336 --> 01:13:48,194
你应该知道...
You should know...

753
01:13:49,500 --> 01:13:52,003
当你杀他的时候 他很困惑
he was very confused when you killed him.

754
01:13:52,034 --> 01:13:54,891
我难以相信Jacob会感到困惑
I seriously doubt that Jacob was ever confused.

755
01:13:54,923 --> 01:13:57,338
我不是说Jacob
I'm not talking about Jacob.

756
01:13:59,529 --> 01:14:01,863
我是说John Locke
I'm talking about John Locke.

757
01:14:04,240 --> 01:14:07,475
你想知道他那时在想什么吗 当你...
Do you wanna know what he was thinking while you...

758
01:14:07,917 --> 01:14:10,624
残忍地勒死他的时候 Benjamin?
choked the life out of him, Benjamin?

759
01:14:10,655 --> 01:14:14,025
他临死前头脑中想的是什么?
What the last thought that ran through his head was?

760
01:14:14,056 --> 01:14:17,965
"我不明白"
"I don't understand."

761
01:14:20,793 --> 01:14:23,685
这是否是你听过的最可怜的事情?
Isn't that just the saddest thing you ever heard?

762
01:14:26,169 --> 01:14:28,341
不过 从某方面看 这也讲得过去
But it's fitting in a way.

763
01:14:28,344 --> 01:14:31,232
因为John第一次踏上这小岛的时候
Because when John first came to the island,

764
01:14:31,274 --> 01:14:33,849
他是一个内心极度悲伤的人
he was a very sad man.

765
01:14:33,881 --> 01:14:35,653
一位受害者
A victim

766
01:14:35,684 --> 01:14:38,854
在得知自己力有不及时 伤心欲绝...
shouting at the world for being told what he couldn't do...

767
01:14:38,886 --> 01:14:40,981
即使这是事实
even though they were right.

768
01:14:42,013 --> 01:14:43,797
他软弱
He was weak

769
01:14:43,828 --> 01:14:48,605
可悲 内心支零破碎
and pathetic and irreparably broken.

770
01:14:49,436 --> 01:14:52,566
但是尽管如此
But despite all that,

771
01:14:52,597 --> 01:14:55,246
他仍有闪光之处
there was something admirable about him.

772
01:14:55,277 --> 01:14:59,698
他是众人中 唯一一个不愿离开小岛的人
He was the only one of them who didn't want to leave.

773
01:14:59,729 --> 01:15:01,888
唯一一个意识到
The only one who realized

774
01:15:01,919 --> 01:15:05,237
他已抛弃的岛外生活是
how pitiful the life he'd left behind

775
01:15:05,279 --> 01:15:07,800
多么地可悲
actually was.

776
01:15:12,255 --> 01:15:13,488
嗯
Hmm.

777
01:15:16,200 --> 01:15:18,004
你想要什么?
What do you want?

778
01:15:18,846 --> 01:15:21,287
这个 极具讽刺意味 Ben
Well, that's the great irony here, Ben,

779
01:15:21,328 --> 01:15:22,337
因为...
because...

780
01:15:22,968 --> 01:15:26,638
我想要的 是John Locke唯一不想要的
I want the one thing that John Locke didn't.

781
01:15:28,379 --> 01:15:32,800
我要回家
I want to go home.

782
01:15:44,473 --> 01:15:46,345
再见 兄弟
Goodbye, dude.

783
01:15:46,887 --> 01:15:49,051
你要是想说会儿话
If you ever wanna talk,

784
01:15:50,693 --> 01:15:52,538
我就在旁边
I'm around.

785
01:16:01,967 --> 01:16:02,931
什么?
What?

786
01:16:05,851 --> 01:16:06,850
没什么
Nothing.

787
01:16:21,966 --> 01:16:23,620
嘿
Hey.

788
01:16:26,090 --> 01:16:27,634
我们在哪?
Where are we?

789
01:16:29,076 --> 01:16:31,065
在寺庙里
We're in a temple.

790
01:16:31,297 --> 01:16:34,075
我们再次被The Others抓了
We got caught by The Others again.

791
01:16:34,206 --> 01:16:34,966
是啊
Yeah.

792
01:16:35,008 --> 01:16:39,093
只有这次 他们是在保护我们
Only this time, they're protecting us.

793
01:16:39,135 --> 01:16:42,020
我这样认为
I think.

794
01:16:42,051 --> 01:16:43,351
当然了
Of course they are.

795
01:16:43,383 --> 01:16:45,145
你还好吗?
You all right?

796
01:16:52,200 --> 01:16:54,176
十分抱歉
I'm so sorry.

797
01:17:09,255 --> 01:17:11,757
你知道你在舱门那里说了什么吗?
You know what you said back at the hatch?

798
01:17:12,488 --> 01:17:14,828
他只是想帮助我们
He's just trying to help us.

799
01:17:16,361 --> 01:17:18,821
我不会杀死Jack
I am not gonna kill Jack.

800
01:17:21,666 --> 01:17:23,472
他理应坐在这块岩石上自我谴责
He deserves to suffer on this rock

801
01:17:23,545 --> 01:17:26,621
和我们其余的人一样
just like the rest of us.

802
01:17:30,225 --> 01:17:31,342
是啊
Yeah.

803
01:17:32,473 --> 01:17:36,607
我知道 而且... 你以为我能预知这事的发生吗?
I know, and... you think I knew this was gonna happen?

804
01:17:37,048 --> 01:17:40,121
我这么快计划好 就是因为想要结束它
I scheduled it so soon because want to get it over with.

805
01:17:40,162 --> 01:17:42,402
所有乘客请注意...
Attention all passengers...

806
01:17:43,044 --> 01:17:44,008
我不知道 妈妈
I don't know, Mom.

807
01:17:44,039 --> 01:17:46,379
他没在这里 所以我不知道让你跟他们如何解释
He's not here, so I can't tell you what to tell them,

808
01:17:46,452 --> 01:17:50,354
只能告诉你 我们没有他办不了事情
other than we can't have the service without him.

809
01:17:50,396 --> 01:17:51,743
嗯
Yeah.

810
01:17:52,074 --> 01:17:55,488
如果有新消息 我会打电话给你的
I will call you if I hear anything.

811
01:17:57,400 --> 01:17:58,818
你掉了什么?
What did you lose?

812
01:18:00,455 --> 01:18:01,831
你说什么?
Excuse me?

813
01:18:02,123 --> 01:18:05,387
哦 他们弄丢了我一个包 你呢?
Oh, they lost one of my bags. What about you?

814
01:18:07,287 --> 01:18:09,234
要是我告诉你 你肯定不会信
You wouldn't believe me if I told you.

815
01:18:09,966 --> 01:18:10,903
试试呗
Try me.

816
01:18:12,719 --> 01:18:15,299
他们弄丢了我爸爸
They lost my father.

817
01:18:16,441 --> 01:18:17,762
什么?
I'm sorry?

818
01:18:18,004 --> 01:18:19,839
他几天前在澳大利亚过世
He died in Australia a couple days ago,

819
01:18:19,901 --> 01:18:23,094
然后 呃 我坐飞机来接他的遗体
and, um, I flew down to get him.

820
01:18:27,703 --> 01:18:29,868
节哀顺变
My condolences.

821
01:18:30,109 --> 01:18:30,792
哎
Yo.

822
01:18:30,834 --> 01:18:33,063
棺材本应在悉尼上机
The coffin was supposed to go on the plane in Sydney,

823
01:18:33,094 --> 01:18:34,786
然而却没有
but it didn't.

824
01:18:34,858 --> 01:18:36,308
显然 他被落在了运输途中
Apparently, he's somewhere in transit,

825
01:18:36,391 --> 01:18:37,359
他们敷衍说
which is their way of saying

826
01:18:37,432 --> 01:18:40,491
他们不知道他究竟在哪里
they have no idea where the hell he is.

827
01:18:40,575 --> 01:18:42,730
呃 他们怎么会知道呢?
Well, how could they know?

828
01:18:43,903 --> 01:18:45,482
是他们核准棺材登机的
They're the ones that checked him in.

829
01:18:45,524 --> 01:18:47,286
我是说 他们肯定有什么追踪系统
I mean, they've gotta have some kind of tracking system.

830
01:18:47,301 --> 01:18:49,069
不 我不是在说棺材
No, I'm not talking about the coffin.

831
01:18:49,142 --> 01:18:52,051
我是说 他们怎么知道他在哪里?
I mean, how could they know where he is?

832
01:18:54,038 --> 01:18:58,368
他们没弄丢你爸爸 他们只是弄丢了他的遗体
They didn't lose your father. They just lost his body.

833
01:19:10,300 --> 01:19:13,024
不管怎样 你比我惨
Either way, your story beats the hell out of mine.

834
01:19:13,065 --> 01:19:15,618
我包里不过是一捆刀
All that was in my suitcase was a bunch of knives.

835
01:19:15,659 --> 01:19:16,706
谢谢
Thanks.

836
01:19:16,738 --> 01:19:18,461
你是推销员?
You some kind of salesman?

837
01:19:18,492 --> 01:19:21,081
嗯 差不多
Yeah, somethin' like that.

838
01:19:23,157 --> 01:19:27,379
呃 很高兴和你聊天 我... 我希望你能找到那具棺材
Well, it's nice talking to you. I... I hope you find that coffin.

839
01:19:28,121 --> 01:19:29,549
我希望你能找到你的刀
I hope you find your knives.

840
01:19:29,581 --> 01:19:30,574
嗯 谢谢
Yeah, thanks.

841
01:19:31,305 --> 01:19:33,776
介意我问下 你发生了什么事么?
Mind if I ask what happened to you?

842
01:19:35,417 --> 01:19:38,350
抱歉 之所以有这一问 是因为我是个脊椎外科医生
I'm sorry. I'm only asking because I'm a spinal surgeon.

843
01:19:38,381 --> 01:19:39,340
我... 我不是想...
I... I didn't mean to...

844
01:19:39,403 --> 01:19:42,194
哦 不 别介意 呃...
Oh, no, don't worry about it. Uh...

845
01:19:42,335 --> 01:19:44,692
呃 手术对我没用
Uh, surgery isn't gonna do anythg to help me.

846
01:19:44,734 --> 01:19:47,580
呃 我这情况回天乏术
Uh, my condition is irreversible.

847
01:19:47,622 --> 01:19:50,310
万事皆有转机
Nothing's irreversible.

848
01:19:56,574 --> 01:19:57,760
呃...
Um...

849
01:19:59,200 --> 01:20:04,414
如果你还想咨询一下的话... 就 呃 给我打个电话
If you ever want a consult... just, uh, give me a call.

850
01:20:06,082 --> 01:20:07,857
这是我家里的电话
It's on the house.

851
01:20:08,299 --> 01:20:09,849
嗯 谢谢
Well, thanks.

852
01:20:11,880 --> 01:20:13,790
你叫Jack Shephard
Jack Shephard.

853
01:20:13,821 --> 01:20:15,922
我叫John John Locke
I'm John. John Locke.

854
01:20:16,864 --> 01:20:20,266
- 很高兴认识你 John - 彼此 彼此
- It's nice to meet you, John. - Nice to meet you, too.

855
01:20:23,950 --> 01:20:25,892
- 谢谢 - 不客气
- Thanks. - You're welcome.

856
01:20:35,135 --> 01:20:37,012
那到底是什么?
What the hell is that?

857
01:20:59,349 --> 01:21:01,229
别开枪! 别杀他!
Don't shoot him! Don't shoot him!

858
01:21:03,975 --> 01:21:05,825
明明该眼见为实
I'm seein' it,

859
01:21:06,456 --> 01:21:08,827
但我却不敢置信
but I'm still not believin' it.

860
01:21:12,400 --> 01:21:14,244
你好 Richard
Hello, Richard.

861
01:21:15,775 --> 01:21:18,030
很高兴看见你摆脱了那些锁链
It's good to see you out of those chains.

862
01:21:23,712 --> 01:21:24,537
是你?
You?

863
01:21:25,078 --> 01:21:25,621
是我
Me.

864
01:21:38,995 --> 01:21:44,265
我对你们每一个人... 都很失望
I am very disappointed... in all of you.

865
01:22:27,963 --> 01:22:29,367
你是Shephard?
You're Shephard?

866
01:22:29,409 --> 01:22:33,246
- 嗯 - 我们需要和你单独谈谈
- Yeah. - We need to speak to you privately.

867
01:22:35,570 --> 01:22:38,299
如果你有话要跟我说 直说就是
If you've got something to say to me, then say it.

868
01:22:38,299 --> 01:22:39,875
否则 就别烦我
Otherwise, just leave me alone.

869
01:22:40,516 --> 01:22:42,233
我想你还没搞明白状况
I don't think you're understanding me here.

870
01:22:42,564 --> 01:22:44,497
我是礼貌相邀
I'm asking politely.

871
01:22:44,639 --> 01:22:47,575
要么你起来 然后乖乖跟我们走
You either get up and come with us on your own,

872
01:22:47,607 --> 01:22:49,730
要么我就把你拖出去
or I'll have you dragged out.

873
01:22:49,761 --> 01:22:51,532
因为我们得好好谈谈
Because we are going to have this conversation,

874
01:22:51,563 --> 01:22:55,873
- 但不在这里谈 - 这样行了吧?
- and it's not going to be here. - Is that right?

875
01:23:03,729 --> 01:23:04,927
Jack啊!
Jack!

876
01:23:06,595 --> 01:23:08,140
哦 老天啊
Oh, my God.

877
01:23:18,757 --> 01:23:20,603
发生了什么事...

What happen...

